  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要给团队整理一份 sed 速查手册，核心围绕 Education_GradeSync 项目里常用的正则处理场景。我想用思维导图的形式，从根节点展开三个主要分支：正则类型、输入来源和操作类型。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root(Education_GradeSync)",
        "Type of regular exprenssions",
        "Input",
        "Operations"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，根节点叫 Education_GradeSync。关于正则类型，我看到你写的是 \"exprenssions\"，这是有意保留的拼写还是笔误？另外需要区分 Regular 和 Extended 两种模式对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Type of regular exprenssions",
        "Regular",
        "Extended",
        "--regexp-extended"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "\"exprenssions\" 是故意保留的，对应我们内部文档的历史写法。对的，Extended 下面要挂上 --regexp-extended 这个参数。现在来看 Input 分支，需要覆盖三种场景：管道输入、直接读文件，还有原地修改。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "From pipe",
        "From file",
        "In-file",
        "cat my_file.txt | sed do_something",
        "sed do_something my_file.txt",
        "sed --in-place do_something my_file.txt"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，Input 分支已添加。管道输入的例子我用 cat my_file.txt | sed do_something，文件直接读取用 sed do_something my_file.txt，原地修改加上 --in-place 参数。接下来 Operations 部分怎么展开？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Input",
        "From pipe",
        "From file",
        "In-file"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Operations 分两大块：Filtering 和 Substitution。Filtering 用 --quiet 配合 /p 标志，只打印匹配行。Substitution 要给出两种形式，一种是纯替换，另一种是替换后同时打印。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Operations",
        "Filtering",
        "Substitution",
        "sed --quiet \"/my_regex/p\"",
        "sed \"s/my_regex/my_replacement/\"",
        "sed \"s/my_regex/my_replacement/p\""
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下细节：Filtering 节点下挂 sed --quiet \"/my_regex/p\"，Substitution 下挂两条命令，分别是 s/my_regex/my_replacement/ 和带 p 标志的版本。这样结构就完整了，我检查一下拼写——根节点你写的是 \"Education_GradeSync\" 后面多了一个右括号？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "root(Education_GradeSync))",
        "Filtering",
        "Substitution"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "啊对，是笔误，根节点应该是 Education_GradeSync 只有一个右括号。另外 \"exprenssions\" 确认保留，\"prenssions\" 也是我们内部的特殊叫法，不用改。",
      "elements_involved": [
